  schema:name "The American Genocide Against the Temporal Middle" ;
  schema:description "The elimination of the temporal middle — the position of inheriting, continuing, and transforming — operates through the same structure as the physical genocide of Indigenous peoples. Physical, epistemic, linguistic, legal, and architectural elimination are the same operation at different scales." ;
